      • addToStart

        public void addToStart(CellPhone aCellPhone)
        addToStart method add a node to the beginning of the list, increasing the size by 1
        参数:

      • insertAtIndex

        public void insertAtIndex(CellPhone a,
                          int index)
        insertAtIndex method insert a node at an index when index is negative or bigger than the size of the list, an exception will be thrown special cases:1.index equals to 0.(invoke addToStart method)
        参数:
        a - an object from CellPhone class
        index - the position

      • deleteFromIndex

        public void deleteFromIndex(int index)
        deleteFromIndex method deletes a node from index when index is negative or bigger than the size of the list, an exception will be thrown special case:1.index is 0 (deleteFromStart method will be executed)
        参数:
        index - the position

      • deleteFromStart

        public void deleteFromStart()
        deleteFromStart method will be tested in deleteFromIndex method

      • replaceAtIndex

        public void replaceAtIndex(CellPhone a,
                           int index)
        replaceAtIndex method replaces a node at given index when index is illegal or the list is empty, do nothing
        参数:
        a - an object from CellPhone class
        index - the position
